               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Directions</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>1. Using a 16 oz mortar and pestle triturate powders well to reduce particle size until uniform. Do not use metal bowls or spatulas while</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>compounding this product.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>2.  Using a 300 capsule machine encapsulate triturate powder mixture into number 1 red capsules<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
